### Production Deployment Prep
#### [NEW] [DEPLOYMENT.md](file:///home/dhruv/sem4/DBMS/EnsureVault/DEPLOYMENT.md)
- Step-by-step instructions on deploying the [docker-compose.yml](file:///home/dhruv/sem4/DBMS/EnsureVault/docker-compose.yml) to an AWS EC2 or DigitalOcean droplet. includes steps for detached runs, port mappings, and domain setups.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `docker-compose up -d --build` to see if the DB compiles the new script without errors.
- Test the FAST API `/chat` endpoint via cURL or Swagger.

### Manual Verification
- Log into the MySQL container `docker exec -it ensurevault-db mysql -u root -p` and test the permissions of `dba_admin`, `data_analyst`, and `claims_processor`.
- Open the Next.js frontend on `localhost:3000`, interact with the AI Chat widget, and ensure it correctly responds or mocks the responses.
